These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-7-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  social-worker, dressmaker, electrician, musician, project-manager, mechanic, firefighter
There are 7 different nationalities: american, brazilian, french, german, mexican, russian, spanish
 1. the electrician is on the far left##1
 2. the musician is not the russian##6
 3. the american is on the left of the dressmaker##1
 4. the spanish is somewhere to the right of the mexican##5
 5. the project-manager is on the left or right of the firefighter##3
 6. the american is on the right of the electrician##1
 7. the mechanic is somewhere between the dressmaker and the brazilian##7
 8. the brazilian is on the left of the spanish##1
 9. the german is somewhere between the project-manager and the french##7
10. the french is on the left or right of the american##3
11. the mexican is on the far left##1
12. the musician is somewhere to the left of the spanish##5
13. the musician is somewhere to the right of the mechanic##5
14. the firefighter is somewhere to the right of the project-manager##5
15. the project-manager is the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4     |     5     |     6     |    7    |
| Job          | electrician    | social-worker    | dressmaker | mechanic | musician | project-manager    | firefighter |
| Nationality   | mexican | american | french  | russian   | german    | brazilian | spanish |

