 1. the owner of the snake is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the owner of the rat##2
 2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##5
 3. the owner of the chinchilla is not the person who's hobby is skydiving##6
 4. the owner of the mouse is somewhere to the right of the owner of the frog##5
 5. the owner of the mouse is between the owner of the frog and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
 6. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
 7. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
 9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere between the owner of the cat and the owner of the snake##7
10. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##3
11. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in an even position##4
12. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not the owner of the mouse##6
13. the person who's hobby is traveling is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is sudoku##7
14. the owner of the ferret is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
15. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
16. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not the owner of the frog##6
17. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3
18. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
