 7. the person driving the scooter is somewhere between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the snowmobile##7
 8. the canadian is on the far left##1
 9. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the left of the american##5
10. the egyptian is in an even position##4
11. the egyptian is somewhere between the indonesian and the indian##7
12. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the right of the pakistani##5
13. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
14. the nigerian is somewhere to the left of the person driving the van##5
15. the pakistani is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
16. the person driving the snowmobile is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5
